    "body": "No progress made, still digging. The hitboxes which exist in draggable_region are correct.  However, the mouse coordinates are not. Since my resolution is set to 150%, I can get the proper coordinates by multiplying the x and y by 1.5.  I'm trying to find the code which is capturing the mouse coordinates, to understand why it's capturing them wrong.\n"
